(43, 3, 26, 43, 1, 15, 15, NULL, 'Witness of John the Baptist', 'Both passages emphasize John''s role as a witness to Jesus. In John 3:26, John''s followers note that many are coming to Jesus, while John 1:15 highlights John''s declaration that Jesus is preferred before him.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
